it.polimi.se2018.view.cli

Class CliPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.view.cli.CliPrinter

  • public class CliPrinter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the necessary print methods for the CliDisplayer and directs them to the indicated PrintStream. The print methods are used to print the Model's elements on a command line environment.
    Author:
    giorgiolabate
